Getting all items from google reader :
http://www.google.com/reader/atom/feed/http://chanceswithwolves.blogspot.com/feeds/posts/default?n=1000
But it implies being connected to google reader for using the API...

Stack Overflow about old items :
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/576552/how-do-i-fetch-all-old-items-on-an-rss-feed

Steps :
- create list of file to download
	intersection btw downloaded episodes and available episodes
- create a bijection btw file name (or metadata) and xml entry
- thread for downloading file, include metadata
